8-07T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"你講緊死左定未死果個？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82f3b5b9965529c4e88eccab3da29f8f9cbf739","tid":770380,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:09:59.000Z","msg":"佢啲文寫得幾舒服"},{"pid":"84b536aa75f50af0385c2b8c3d1e7528e8a6237f","tid":770380,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"美國唔係唔比你發展高科技<br />\n只不過唔比你偷佢野<br />\n你要發展可以自己研發"},{"pid":"1c19dc663545822c2237c78fd6fa7fafedcae111","tid":770380,"uid":42764,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">在沒有工會約束的環境下，從事建築行業的人一般懂得幾方面，不像西方那樣分門別類，河水不許犯井水。結果是懂得設計機電的人才無數，而從基建工程到樓房建築，中國造得好而快。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n所以中國永遠出唔到頂尖專家，勁既人會浪費時間學多幾樣野，無一樣做到頂尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae44261c699c22a785c5be2fa7f651aea6f47b96","tid":770380,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"支那種總係有舖蟈屍癮既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552f26e73c5892c2dfe07f100ef56822828e9ca1","tid":770380,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5e6446de18ed70438016f8591268f1c31e333a8","tid":770380,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51c534b3c88ee1d9b8ec0e3e96f01b8b70e37c6e","tid":770380,"uid":39800,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"張五常是咪同陳雲係兄弟嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:15:36.000Z","msg":"陳雲有講過話幾受張五常影響"},{"pid":"fa36f360018e4342a419b39e4f13c17eec2e071a","tid":770380,"uid":42042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"FACT: 張五常長居深圳"},{"pid":"6be709ede710ddb8f7c8af317f6acb83a3b19f63","tid":770380,"uid":23180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"以共奴國性格，搞多鑊文革鎖國，死番7-8億人拆鳩晒D野再黎過咪仲快"},{"pid":"746937bfb02d73054ce0eb371f46171108fd12fc","tid":770380,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5e6446de18ed70438016f8591268f1c31e333a8","tid":770380,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51c534b3c88ee1d9b8ec0e3e96f01b8b70e37c6e","tid":770380,"uid":39800,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"張五常是咪同陳雲係兄弟嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:15:36.000Z","msg":"陳雲有講過話幾受張五常影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"兩個都ON LUN <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f3cebf61dca2f548a647b650a8c6861e36e307","tid":770380,"uid":38785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"支那淨係入口人哋啲高科技產品組裝再出口，可以同印度比？<br />\n<br />\n另外佢話最低市值工資比印度高一倍，越南兩倍，非洲三倍，即係人工支出比人高，點站在舒適位置，唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f53e90b5340ec756da490ccd59f400a1afbbfa3","tid":770380,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ea4d58e893bb6806de46434a6d89cbf9447817","tid":770380,"uid":4783,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"張五常就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國唔係唔俾你發展高科技，只係你現有既科技都係偷人而黎，人地要停止姐<br />\n不論係間諜偷，還是留學生學完去偷，去人地研究室偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且中國平價日常用品根本已經變左myth<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知幾耐無見過，仲有得拎黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d42491a7ae7f6c32